               Clipboard      bits of text you have put in the
               History        clipboard.  So use Ctrl-V to paste the
                              current contents of the clipboard, but
                              Ctrl-Shft-V to view the history of past
                              contents of the clipboard; then hit
                              Return to select the bit you want to
                              paste.

Ctrl-@         Insert char    Insert literally the next character
                              typed, even if it is a control character.

